data.description: Step into the perfect starter home! This wonderful residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and an additional bonus room, offering a blend of space, versatility, and comfort. This design creates a welcoming ambiance that suits various lifestyles. The 3 bedrooms provide flexibility for a growing family, a dedicated home office, or cozy guest rooms. But that's not all – this home comes with a fantastic bonus room, a versatile space that could serve as a playroom, entertainment hub, or even a home gym. The standout feature of this home is the expansive fenced backyard. Imagine weekend gatherings, playtime with pets, or simply enjoying the tranquility of your private outdoor retreat. Situated in a friendly neighborhood with convenient access to local amenities and quick commute. Don't miss the chance to make this 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem with a bonus room and a large fenced backyard your perfect home sweet home! $5,000 for the buyer to use however they choose!Highly motivated seller!
